WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.909
Good morning, family. How are you

00:00:02.909 --> 00:00:02.919
all

00:00:02.919 --> 00:00:05.349
doing today? I have some things on

00:00:05.359 --> 00:00:08.190
my heart. I found this prophetic

00:00:08.200 --> 00:00:11.150
word from Kent Christmas

00:00:11.160 --> 00:00:13.829
and a dream from Dana

00:00:13.839 --> 00:00:16.470
Coverstone. The Lord has really put

00:00:16.480 --> 00:00:18.870
Pastor Dana Coverstone on my heart—specifically some

00:00:18.880 --> 00:00:21.150
of the things He has shown him in

00:00:21.160 --> 00:00:24.109
these dreams. I've

00:00:24.119 --> 00:00:26.230
been going back through

00:00:26.240 --> 00:00:29.070
some of the past dreams

00:00:29.070 --> 00:00:29.080
from

00:00:29.080 --> 00:00:32.510
basically three or four years ago.

00:00:32.520 --> 00:00:36.910
I really

00:00:36.920 --> 00:00:38.950
believe he heard the Lord on

00:00:38.950 --> 00:00:38.960
many

00:00:38.960 --> 00:00:39.950
of

00:00:39.950 --> 00:00:39.960
those;

00:00:39.960 --> 00:00:42.750
some can be prayed away,

00:00:42.760 --> 00:00:46.229
and some can't. The videos

00:00:46.239 --> 00:00:48.990
I'm going to show you are very

00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:51.549
important because they go alongside what

00:00:51.559 --> 00:00:54.069
the Lord showed me about the plague

00:00:54.079 --> 00:00:57.270
that's coming and the economic collapse.

00:01:03.799 --> 00:01:06.830
Before this year is out, the death

00:01:06.840 --> 00:01:10.510
angel is being loosed upon the Earth.

00:01:10.520 --> 00:01:13.149
What they concocted and created in

00:01:13.159 --> 00:01:16.270
laboratories called Coronavirus will

00:01:16.280 --> 00:01:19.710
pale in comparison, saith the Lord, to

00:01:19.720 --> 00:01:21.710
the spirit that the death angel will

00:01:21.720 --> 00:01:25.630
loose upon the nations. It will not

00:01:25.640 --> 00:01:28.910
touch My people. For the first virus,

00:01:28.920 --> 00:01:31.390
the enemy brought

00:01:31.390 --> 00:01:31.400
it

00:01:31.400 --> 00:01:34.590
against the innocent and the old, but

00:01:34.600 --> 00:01:37.389
this, saith God, will not touch the

00:01:37.399 --> 00:01:40.310
church. Some will fall on your right hand,

00:01:40.320 --> 00:01:43.389
as I declared in Psalm 91, and

00:01:43.399 --> 00:01:45.670
they will fall on your left hand, but

00:01:45.680 --> 00:01:49.230
it shall not come nigh unto thy dwelling.

00:01:49.240 --> 00:01:51.510
What you just saw was him saying

00:01:51.520 --> 00:01:53.990
a thousand shall fall at your

00:01:54.000 --> 00:01:56.270
side and ten thousand at your right hand.

00:02:30.400 --> 00:02:32.910
If you remember what I said,

00:02:32.920 --> 00:02:35.030
it goes alongside what the Lord

00:02:35.040 --> 00:02:38.430
showed me about

00:02:38.440 --> 00:02:42.350
a glow of honey around the

00:02:42.360 --> 00:02:45.070
believers. We would go

00:02:45.080 --> 00:02:48.350
in and lay hands on people

00:02:48.350 --> 00:02:48.360
in

00:02:48.360 --> 00:02:51.750
cots. I saw cots full of bodies

00:02:51.760 --> 00:02:53.710
and people

00:02:53.720 --> 00:02:55.589
dying of this virus; it was very

00:02:55.599 --> 00:02:58.990
tragic.

00:02:59.000 --> 00:03:01.430
I've told

00:03:01.430 --> 00:03:01.440
everyone

00:03:01.440 --> 00:03:03.350
about what the Lord showed me, so I

00:03:03.350 --> 00:03:03.360
won't

00:03:03.360 --> 00:03:05.030
go over it

00:03:05.030 --> 00:03:05.040
all again.

00:03:05.040 --> 00:03:07.789
I'm just

00:03:07.799 --> 00:03:09.149
showing

00:03:09.159 --> 00:03:11.670
you that there are prophetic voices hearing that

00:03:11.680 --> 00:03:13.589
another

00:03:13.599 --> 00:03:16.830
plague and pestilence are coming.

00:03:19.560 --> 00:03:20.910
The Lord was also talking to me about

00:03:20.920 --> 00:03:22.149
getting in shape. I've been

00:03:22.159 --> 00:03:23.869
lifting weights, trying to

00:03:23.879 --> 00:03:26.630
bulk up and take care of my body more.

00:03:26.640 --> 00:03:29.110
It's been a challenge

00:03:29.110 --> 00:03:29.120
balancing

00:03:29.120 --> 00:03:30.830
eating with

00:03:30.840 --> 00:03:33.710
working out,

00:03:36.710 --> 00:03:36.720
but

00:03:38.799 --> 00:03:40.309
I'm

00:03:40.319 --> 00:03:41.869
learning a lot on YouTube.

00:03:43.680 --> 00:03:45.110
My family were not

00:03:45.120 --> 00:03:46.630
people who worked out,

00:03:46.640 --> 00:03:50.830
so this is all

00:03:50.830 --> 00:03:50.840
new. This

00:03:50.840 --> 00:03:53.589
is Bonnie Jones,

00:03:53.599 --> 00:03:58.830
Bob Jones's widow. I

00:03:58.840 --> 00:04:01.309
believe she hears the Lord, and

00:04:01.319 --> 00:04:05.390
she got a

00:04:05.400 --> 00:04:06.910
prophetic visitation

00:04:09.040 --> 00:04:10.910
about a week ago. This is a fresh

00:04:10.920 --> 00:04:13.990
video where the Lord

00:04:13.990 --> 00:04:14.000
gave

00:04:14.000 --> 00:04:17.469
her a very stern prophetic

00:04:17.479 --> 00:04:19.909
warning.

00:04:22.280 --> 00:04:25.790
She

00:04:27.560 --> 00:04:31.670
heard, 'Beware the dragon,'followed by 'biological warfare.'She associated the dragon

00:04:31.670 --> 00:04:31.680
with

00:04:31.680 --> 00:04:33.430
China.

00:04:33.440 --> 00:04:36.950
Biological warfare

00:04:36.960 --> 00:04:40.790
is

00:04:45.199 --> 00:04:48.070
the deliberate

00:04:48.080 --> 00:04:51.790
use of disease-causing agents

00:04:51.790 --> 00:04:51.800
like

00:04:51.800 --> 00:04:54.550
bacteria or toxins

00:04:54.560 --> 00:04:57.950
to kill or

00:04:57.950 --> 00:04:57.960
incapacitate

00:04:57.960 --> 00:05:01.629
as an act of war. I believe

00:05:01.639 --> 00:05:04.950
China is cooking up another virus

00:05:04.960 --> 00:05:07.990
that will be more deadly.

00:05:10.360 --> 00:05:12.790
Remember when I told you I

00:05:12.800 --> 00:05:16.710
saw the dragon?

00:05:22.919 --> 00:05:27.110
In my

00:05:27.120 --> 00:05:30.270
World War II video, I said the dragon was

00:05:30.270 --> 00:05:30.280
hiding

00:05:30.280 --> 00:05:32.830
behind a black rock,

00:05:32.840 --> 00:05:35.390
waiting for a new season.

00:05:35.400 --> 00:05:38.430
The dragon represented

00:05:38.440 --> 00:05:41.390
the

00:05:41.400 --> 00:05:43.150
COVID.

00:05:43.160 --> 00:05:46.150
I was shown in the spirit that they were

00:05:46.160 --> 00:05:48.309
taking a biological

00:05:48.309 --> 00:05:48.319
agent

00:05:48.319 --> 00:05:49.950
in a lab

00:05:49.960 --> 00:05:51.909
to release on the people,

00:05:51.919 --> 00:05:54.590
starting

00:05:54.600 --> 00:05:58.189
in Europe. I warned

00:05:58.199 --> 00:05:59.629
about that

00:05:59.629 --> 00:05:59.639
in

00:05:59.639 --> 00:06:01.029
a

00:06:01.039 --> 00:06:03.710
video called 'The Dream That I

00:06:03.720 --> 00:06:06.350
Had.'Back

00:06:06.360 --> 00:06:09.710
in April, the Lord told me

00:06:09.720 --> 00:06:12.870
He was sending another plague and that cataclysmic things would happen. He said a line

00:06:12.870 --> 00:06:12.880
of demarcation

00:06:12.880 --> 00:06:14.870
has been drawn.

00:06:14.870 --> 00:06:14.880
Calamity is

00:06:14.880 --> 00:06:16.990
coming because of disobedience

00:06:16.990 --> 00:06:17.000
to His word. Famine

00:06:17.000 --> 00:06:19.670
is

00:06:19.670 --> 00:06:19.680
imminent—not

00:06:19.680 --> 00:06:21.870
just

00:06:21.880 --> 00:06:25.350
of

00:06:25.350 --> 00:06:25.360
food,

00:06:25.360 --> 00:06:27.350
but

00:06:27.360 --> 00:06:29.830
of

00:06:29.830 --> 00:06:29.840
the

00:06:29.840 --> 00:06:30.950
Word.

00:06:30.960 --> 00:06:34.749
There has been a chokehold

00:06:34.749 --> 00:06:34.759
in America,

00:06:34.759 --> 00:06:38.469
and now

00:06:42.680 --> 00:06:47.589
He

00:06:53.120 --> 00:06:57.350
is

00:07:11.800 --> 00:07:14.110
going to release it.

00:07:14.120 --> 00:07:16.909
I'm not 100% sure what He

00:07:16.909 --> 00:07:16.919
means by

00:07:16.919 --> 00:07:19.230
a famine

00:07:19.240 --> 00:07:22.710
of food,

00:07:26.869 --> 00:07:26.879
but

00:07:29.560 --> 00:07:31.909
catastrophes

00:07:31.909 --> 00:07:31.919
like

00:07:31.919 --> 00:07:34.950
earthquakes,

00:07:34.960 --> 00:07:38.950
floods, and fires

00:07:51.599 --> 00:07:53.309
will

00:07:55.360 --> 00:07:58.670
affect our food chain.

00:07:58.680 --> 00:08:00.350
In

00:08:00.360 --> 00:08:02.869
a

00:08:02.879 --> 00:08:04.990
vision,

00:08:05.000 --> 00:08:08.830
I saw

00:08:08.840 --> 00:08:11.110
John Deere tractors

00:08:11.120 --> 00:08:14.350
sitting

00:08:14.350 --> 00:08:14.360
idle

00:08:14.360 --> 00:08:17.189
with

00:08:17.189 --> 00:08:17.199
no

00:08:17.199 --> 00:08:19.230
crops

00:08:19.230 --> 00:08:19.240
planted

00:08:19.240 --> 00:08:21.670
from the West Coast to the East Coast. There was

00:08:21.670 --> 00:08:21.680
an

00:08:21.680 --> 00:08:26.390
extreme

00:08:26.400 --> 00:08:27.950
drought. The Lord said

00:08:30.159 --> 00:08:31.950
three

00:08:31.960 --> 00:08:34.829
times, 'There's no water.'I saw the

00:08:34.829 --> 00:08:34.839
Lubbock

00:08:34.839 --> 00:08:38.230
area, Texas, and through Mexico

00:08:38.230 --> 00:08:38.240
where

00:08:38.240 --> 00:08:40.949
it was

00:08:40.949 --> 00:08:40.959
extremely

00:08:40.959 --> 00:08:42.829
dry.

00:09:10.440 --> 00:09:12.790
We need to

00:09:12.800 --> 00:09:17.389
be wise, not fearful.

00:09:18.240 --> 00:09:21.190
We cannot stop judgment,

00:09:21.200 --> 00:09:24.230
but we can lessen

00:09:24.240 --> 00:09:26.069
it through

00:09:26.069 --> 00:09:26.079
prayer.

00:09:26.079 --> 00:09:29.670
Jesus

00:09:29.670 --> 00:09:29.680
told

00:09:29.680 --> 00:09:31.069
me face-to-face that

00:09:36.680 --> 00:09:39.790
this major shaking

00:09:39.800 --> 00:09:41.550
will take place for a humbling and an awakening. We will be a

00:09:47.519 --> 00:09:52.110
sheep nation because

00:09:52.110 --> 00:09:52.120
of

00:09:52.120 --> 00:09:55.750
the

00:09:55.760 --> 00:09:57.949
prayers of our founding

00:09:57.959 --> 00:10:00.710
fathers.

00:10:12.800 --> 00:10:14.790
I've seen

00:10:14.800 --> 00:10:17.030
bridges

00:10:17.040 --> 00:10:18.949
and earthquakes preventing trucks from

00:10:18.949 --> 00:10:18.959
crossing,

00:10:18.959 --> 00:10:21.870
and I've

00:10:21.870 --> 00:10:21.880
seen

00:10:21.880 --> 00:10:24.430
gas shortages.

00:10:59.480 --> 00:11:02.389
Pastor Dana

00:11:02.389 --> 00:11:02.399
also

00:11:02.399 --> 00:11:06.389
had

00:11:06.389 --> 00:11:06.399
a

00:11:06.399 --> 00:11:08.269
dream

00:11:08.269 --> 00:11:08.279
about

00:11:08.279 --> 00:11:10.750
an

00:11:10.750 --> 00:11:10.760
'Economic

00:11:10.760 --> 00:11:11.870
Desert.'He

00:11:11.880 --> 00:11:13.990
was

00:11:13.990 --> 00:11:14.000
at

00:11:16.550 --> 00:11:16.560
the

00:11:16.560 --> 00:11:18.629
bottom

00:11:18.639 --> 00:11:21.910
of an ocean,

00:11:23.279 --> 00:11:26.470
2,000

00:11:28.959 --> 00:11:32.430
feet

00:11:51.720 --> 00:11:54.750
below sea

00:11:54.760 --> 00:11:58.230
level. He saw a billboard that said 'Economic Desert.'He saw life acting normal, then suddenly changing. Cars were parked, trash was

00:12:11.590 --> 00:12:11.600
everywhere,

00:12:29.360 --> 00:12:30.750
and

00:12:48.720 --> 00:12:51.350
people

00:13:07.839 --> 00:13:10.870
were

00:13:26.110 --> 00:13:26.120
carrying

00:13:43.040 --> 00:13:46.069
brown paper

00:13:51.880 --> 00:13:54.269
grocery bags.

00:13:54.279 --> 00:13:56.030
Eventually,

00:13:56.040 --> 00:13:58.230
they

00:14:14.629 --> 00:14:14.639
had

00:14:32.759 --> 00:14:34.189
no

00:14:34.199 --> 00:14:37.870
bags, and ATMs

00:14:37.880 --> 00:14:39.509
were

00:14:42.509 --> 00:14:42.519
empty.

00:14:44.110 --> 00:14:44.120
At

00:14:48.639 --> 00:14:51.150
a checkout line,

00:15:03.800 --> 00:15:05.710
the

00:15:05.720 --> 00:15:07.949
scanner wasn't working, and

00:15:07.949 --> 00:15:07.959
a

00:15:10.670 --> 00:15:10.680
man

00:15:10.680 --> 00:15:13.069
with

00:15:13.079 --> 00:15:14.629
an

00:15:14.639 --> 00:15:16.910
empty

00:15:16.910 --> 00:15:16.920
wallet

00:15:16.920 --> 00:15:19.069
began to cry.

00:15:26.160 --> 00:15:30.470
I'm

00:15:30.480 --> 00:15:34.389
encouraging you

00:15:34.399 --> 00:15:36.069
to build the

00:15:36.079 --> 00:15:37.389
kingdom of God

00:15:37.399 --> 00:15:39.309
and ask

00:15:39.309 --> 00:15:39.319
Him

00:15:39.319 --> 00:15:41.189
what you need to

00:15:41.199 --> 00:15:46.790
do.

00:15:51.360 --> 00:15:54.590
Have some cash

00:15:54.600 --> 00:15:57.949
and

00:15:57.959 --> 00:16:01.990
resources set aside.

00:16:11.120 --> 00:16:15.030
It doesn't have to be a

00:16:15.040 --> 00:16:17.230
lot, but we are headed for

00:16:17.240 --> 00:16:19.590
hard times. I believe

00:16:21.319 --> 00:16:22.829
in miracles,

00:16:22.839 --> 00:16:26.590
but

00:16:26.590 --> 00:16:26.600
Christians

00:16:26.600 --> 00:16:27.629
will

00:16:27.629 --> 00:16:27.639
face

00:16:27.639 --> 00:16:29.189
hard things.

00:16:29.199 --> 00:16:31.509
It's not

00:16:31.519 --> 00:16:34.230
an

00:16:34.230 --> 00:16:34.240
easy-peasy

00:16:34.240 --> 00:16:36.550
life.

00:16:36.550 --> 00:16:36.560
Dana

00:16:38.309 --> 00:16:38.319
also

00:16:38.319 --> 00:16:40.389
had

00:16:40.399 --> 00:16:44.269
a

00:16:44.279 --> 00:16:45.790
dream

00:16:48.079 --> 00:16:50.870
about

00:16:53.880 --> 00:16:57.230
Wall Street

00:16:57.240 --> 00:17:01.470
and

00:17:01.480 --> 00:17:03.509
bartering. He saw people trading chickens

00:17:03.509 --> 00:17:03.519
and tools. One man traded

00:17:03.519 --> 00:17:08.270
shotgun shells

00:17:12.559 --> 00:17:16.069
for

00:17:17.480 --> 00:17:20.789
chickens;

00:18:23.960 --> 00:18:26.190
a

00:19:39.549 --> 00:19:39.559
lady

00:20:49.919 --> 00:20:51.909
traded hammers for

00:20:51.909 --> 00:20:51.919
screws. Someone

00:20:51.919 --> 00:20:54.990
traded

00:21:13.870 --> 00:21:13.880
a

00:21:28.279 --> 00:21:31.789
Rolex

00:21:45.870 --> 00:21:45.880
for

00:22:00.440 --> 00:22:03.510
horses.

00:22:03.520 --> 00:22:05.710
There were no vehicles,

00:22:05.720 --> 00:22:07.269
only

00:22:07.279 --> 00:22:08.950
bikes

00:22:08.950 --> 00:22:08.960
and

00:22:08.960 --> 00:22:10.950
skateboards.

00:22:20.760 --> 00:22:22.029
In

00:22:33.159 --> 00:22:35.230
the

00:22:46.200 --> 00:22:47.789
dream,

00:23:08.480 --> 00:23:11.950
tables

00:23:11.960 --> 00:23:13.870
were bowing under the weight of

00:23:13.870 --> 00:23:13.880
goods

00:23:13.880 --> 00:23:15.590
like

00:23:15.590 --> 00:23:15.600
unwashed

00:23:15.600 --> 00:23:17.549
eggs

00:23:17.559 --> 00:23:20.070
and

00:23:20.080 --> 00:23:21.909
rusty

00:23:21.919 --> 00:23:23.190
hand

00:23:23.200 --> 00:23:25.470
tools. I saw

00:23:25.470 --> 00:23:25.480
wooden

00:23:27.430 --> 00:23:27.440
awls

00:23:29.110 --> 00:23:29.120
and

00:23:29.120 --> 00:23:31.710
hand

00:23:31.720 --> 00:23:33.710
drills,

00:23:33.720 --> 00:23:35.350
but no power tools.

00:24:02.919 --> 00:24:04.830
The man with the shotgun shells

00:24:07.240 --> 00:24:09.029
was barefoot

00:24:09.039 --> 00:24:11.950
and

00:24:13.110 --> 00:24:13.120
used

00:24:15.640 --> 00:24:18.029
his shirt as

00:24:18.029 --> 00:24:18.039
a

00:24:18.039 --> 00:24:19.950
bag.

00:24:25.240 --> 00:24:27.870
A

00:24:31.399 --> 00:24:33.710
man

00:24:52.350 --> 00:24:52.360
representing

00:25:12.320 --> 00:25:15.230
Jesus

00:25:15.240 --> 00:25:16.630
was there

00:25:20.510 --> 00:25:20.520
and

00:25:23.440 --> 00:25:26.269
said, 'You

00:25:26.279 --> 00:25:28.669
are not as prepared as you need to

00:25:28.679 --> 00:25:33.149
be. Hearken to My word. Embrace, don't

00:25:33.159 --> 00:25:37.630
barter with My word, as you will come up

00:25:45.310 --> 00:25:45.320
short.'This

00:25:50.720 --> 00:25:53.389
situation

00:25:58.789 --> 00:25:58.799
might

00:26:02.360 --> 00:26:05.510
last longer

00:26:05.520 --> 00:26:08.070
than you think.

00:26:13.399 --> 00:26:14.510
I

00:26:19.960 --> 00:26:22.669
saw

00:26:27.919 --> 00:26:30.350
four oak

00:26:30.360 --> 00:26:32.430
trees

00:26:32.440 --> 00:26:35.389
representing

00:26:35.399 --> 00:26:38.070
four years.

00:26:55.799 --> 00:26:57.950
People were not ready for the

00:26:57.950 --> 00:26:57.960
first year,

00:26:57.960 --> 00:26:59.630
and by

00:26:59.630 --> 00:26:59.640
the end,

00:26:59.640 --> 00:27:02.310
they were

00:27:23.200 --> 00:27:26.389
bartering for ammo.

00:27:26.399 --> 00:27:28.909
If

00:27:28.919 --> 00:27:32.350
you

